<h2 id="procurement-for-small-and-medium-sized-enterprises">Procurement for small and medium-sized enterprises</h2>

<p>Our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/updated-small-and-medium-sized-enterprises-action-plan-published">small and medium-sized enterprise (<abbr title="small and medium-sized enterprises">SME</abbr>) action plan</a> sets out what we’re doing to make it easier for SMEs to become <abbr title="Department of Health">DH</abbr> suppliers.</p>

